<br>
- MT engages boss-mob<br>
- rampage_war_01 /shield MT to get her to live longer through the initial unslowed onslaught<br>
- /shield runs out after 12 seconds (more if you actually put AA into it)<br>
<br>
Rampage healers would have their hands full while /shield is up, but it would litterally cut in half the damage the MT was taking, hopefully long enough to get a slow in.  Also, the rampage_war_01 could break the shield by activating a /disc (evasive or defensive most likely) if needed.<br>
<br>
Fundemental assumption:  you can /shield someone who has a /disc up (I know you can't /shield if <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>you</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> have a /disc up, but not sure about your target).<br>
<br>
